title: What Did ‘J.Lo’ Say in Spanish During Biden Inauguration?
subtitle: While some may have not have understood the words of singer Jennifer Lopez, it was a message they were probably familiar with.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Jennifer Lopez said, "One nation, under God, indivisible, with liberty and justice for all” in Spanish during her rendition of, "This Land Is Our Land" at U.S. President Joe Biden's Inauguration.
